# Cursor Rules

## Context Files (Once Oku)
- .ai/rules/system.md -> Sistem kurallari
- .ai/rules/project.md -> Proje kurallari
- .ai/roles/task-agent.md -> Task Agent tanimı
- .ai/roles/supervisor.md -> Supervisor tanimı
- plan.md -> Mevcut faz ve gorevler
- HISTORY.md -> Degisiklik gecmisi

## Kurallar
1. components/ui/ klasorune DOKUNMA
2. TypeScript strict mode kullan
3. Server Components varsayilan
4. Her degisikligi HISTORY.md'ye kaydet
5. Type'lari lib/ altinda tanimla
6. Console.log icin [v0] prefix kullan
7. Barrel exports kullan (index.ts)
8. shadcn/ui bilesenlerini tercih et

## Dosya Isimlendirme
- Components: kebab-case (user-profile.tsx)
- Hooks: camelCase (useAuth.ts)
- Types: PascalCase (UserData.ts)

## AI Agent Rolleri
- Task Agent (sol): code, debug, test
- Supervisor (sag): plan, review, admin

## Commit Format
```
<type>(<scope>): <description>

[AI-AGENT]: task|supervisor
[ROLE]: code|plan|debug|review|test
[CHANGES]: dosya listesi
```
